    {
        "content": "<p>Hey everyone. Just passing along more info about the satellite meetings during this year's Dataverse Community Meeting.</p>\n<p>Working group leads interested in meeting in-person and online on May 12 can use the <a href=\"https://dcm2026.com/registration\">DCM2026 registration form</a> to request a meeting for the working group.</p>\n<p>On the registration form, WG leads will need to include a list of in-person attendees, who won't be let in if they haven't registered and aren't on the list, and are responsible for letting group members know about the May 12 meeting and for any marketing for new members.</p>",
        "id": 573556734,
        "sender_full_name": "Julian Gautier",
        "timestamp": 1770911365
    },
    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"621770\">@Julian Gautier</span> thanks!</p>\n<p><span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"660583\">@Dieuwertje Bloemen</span> how does this look? It's a doc to start collecting names of attendees: <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1uQIZtN6yuqH2XlcfRxNKa3KGvbsxT-fHIUZzKOZGR2k/edit?usp=sharing\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1uQIZtN6yuqH2XlcfRxNKa3KGvbsxT-fHIUZzKOZGR2k/edit?usp=sharing</a></p>",
        "id": 573782824,
        "sender_full_name": "Philip Durbin 🚀",
        "timestamp": 1771000087
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>I went ahead and <a href=\"https://github.com/gdcc/www.gdcc.io/commit/df8ac0c7edf651529595701f8ab7662ca23c403f\">added</a> it to our <a href=\"https://www.gdcc.io/working-groups/documentation.html\">web page</a> under a new heading called \"next in-person meeting\"</p>\n<p>It looks like this:</p>\n<p><a href=\"/user_uploads/53090/RWx4zLZovJDGyg4t7PFdup4m/in-person.png\">in-person.png</a></p>\n<div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/53090/RWx4zLZovJDGyg4t7PFdup4m/in-person.png\" title=\"in-person.png\"><img data-original-content-type=\"image/png\" data-original-dimensions=\"769x216\" src=\"/user_uploads/thumbnail/53090/RWx4zLZovJDGyg4t7PFdup4m/in-person.png/840x560.webp\"></a></div>",
